    *   The inaugural title in the Stanford Briefs imprint.
*   *[Common Knowledge? An Ethnography of Wikipedia](/Common_Knowledge%3F_An_Ethnography_of_Wikipedia)*, by [Dariusz Jemielniak](/Dariusz_Jemielniak) (2014), a book about the very ecosystem you are currently inhabiting. How meta.
